data.description: Beautifully well-maintained home in new construction community, Sierra Vista. You'll appreciate the attention to detail that has gone into this home - From the well maintained garden to the beautiful Granite island Kitchen, rich cabinetry, LED lighting and luxury vinyl floors throughout living areas this home has been meticulously cared for. Large primary bed, Open concept formal living dining combo and a spacious backyard with covered patio turn charming home in to the perfect home for the avid entertainer. Enjoy all the amenities the new neighborhood has to offer - Pools, Splash Pads, Picnic Areas, Walking Trails and so much more coming soon! Conveniently located near SH 288, 25 Miles to Downtown Houston, 20 Miles to University of Houston-Clear Lake at Pearland and 44 miles to Galveston Beach! Call now to book your appointment today!
